review_title: the shirt is 60/40 Poly cotton - not 100% cotton as was listed in the bullets
reviews: I really wanted a shirt like this because i have trouble with things fitting - i have wide shoulders; also i wanted something with no seam right on the shoulder because in winter, with several layers; you end up with that many seams digging into your shoulder and collarbone. So, i was very happy to find the 'raglan ' sleeve; and Hanes, as well as 100% cotton. Unfortunately - i cannot wear it because my skin reacts to polyester - but -for those that that is not an issue ; this is a nice comfortable well made and well priced shirt.
product_name: Hanes Men's Long Sleeve Raglan Henley
